{"tid":956526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★高鐵西九站食肆冒煙　消防大陣仗戒備","createTime":"2018-12-26T10:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T11:45:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"759b1da5dc87d5ace2db391c2843d3f23b624c59","tid":956526,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181226/photo/bkn-20181226155159187-1226_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181226161847\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181226%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181226155159187-1226_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181226161847&h=888250e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高鐵西九龍總站B2層美食廣場，今午（26日）2時許，一名食肆男職員在上址煮食，期間疑煮燶食物，發出燶味並有煙冒出，繼而觸動火警鐘。大批消防接報趕至，未有發現火苗及煙，經初步調查後收隊離去，期間，車站服務未受影響，無人受傷亦毋須疏散。<br />\n<br />\n上址於本月15日亦曾發生火警，當日早上6時許，有廚工用電爐炒河粉時，疑鑊氣太猛搶火噴出火球，消防接報到場前，火勢已被自動灑水系統救熄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181226/bkn-20181226155159187-1226_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181226%2Fbkn-20181226155159187-1226_00822_001.html&d=NPvZp18H0kUodnRzH3AML5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=11625066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181226/bkn-20181226155159187-1226_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"150fcef824749ec5888ae38a423fdac19a3fa270","tid":956526,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:43:50.000Z","msg":"冇人理老貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cbbb40544c77518be999bef93d9b9089282733","tid":956526,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:45:41.000Z","msg":"火攻毒蛇陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9756004d3532ac2f229f0990ced28a61efc8b3a5","tid":956526,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"150fcef824749ec5888ae38a423fdac19a3fa270","tid":956526,"uid":1